Enumeration Type Documentation

enum Aeb_Feature_t

Feature of Access Enable Block that can be toggled.

Enumerator
AEB_000_SP_ROM_PARTITION_SEL 

ROM: SPROM secure (1) vs. unsecure (0) partition selection

AEB_001_ALLOW_EXEC_AXI_TRANS 

Intercepts all executable AXI transactions from SP to HSP bus (and the rest of SOCs)

AEB_002_SP_DBGTAP_EN 

JTAG: SW Debug for HSP's SP cores

AEB_003_RNG_DAS_EN 

RNG: Allow RNG DAS mode for raw TRBG collection

AEB_004_BLK_HWCHKPT_LOCKS 

HWCHKPT: Turn-off HSP HW checkpointing (hashing) feature locks

AEB_005_HSP_DFT_EN 

En/Dis JTAG/Scan chain of the HSP (include MBIST, Mdump, todo: list out all DFT tests)

AEB_006_TOP_DFT_EN 

En/dis Master TAP controller for SCANDUMP/DEBUG/IOCONTROL

AEB_007_FUSE_DFT_EN 

JTAG: Enable Fuse Macro DFT Commands from TDR

AEB_008_SS128_TDR_EN 

JTAG: TDR read access to 128-bit security state register

AEB_009_MEM_CHK_DISABLE 

MEM: 1) Disable EDC checks on RAMs. 2) Disable PARITY checks on TCM

AEB_010_ALLOW_EDC_ERR_INJECT 

MEM: Allow EDC error injection

AEB_011_AEBFUSE_PROG_EN 

FCTRL: Program enable for AEB Fuse

AEB_012_SOCID_PROG_EN 

FCTRL: Program enable for the N_SOC_ID

AEB_013_KEY_PROG_EN 

FCTRL: Program enable for the entire key region

AEB_014_RSVD0_PROG_EN 

FCTRL: Program enable for RESERVED0 region

AEB_015_UART_EN 

UART: ability to send and receive UART messages

AEB_016_RSVD1_PROG_EN 

FCTRL: Program enable for all RESERVED1 region

AEB_017_KEY_SENSE_EN 

FCTRL: Sense enable for the Key fuses

AEB_018_OBS_EN 

FCTRL: Obs enable

AEB_019_CPU_BOOT_EN 

Enable CPU Boot Control bit CPUBOOTEN

AEB_020_SP_EN 

allow SP to run

AEB_021_ALLOW_TDR_RESET 

Allow HSP to be Reset via the tdr_hsp_reset register

AEB_022_FATAL_RSTMSK_WEN 

HSP Fatal Error Mask Register (Sticky/Non-Sticky) Write Enable

AEB_023_MPU_PROTECTION_DIS 

Disable MPU protection

AEB_024_MST_DBG 

Enable DBGU : through config reg IF gating

AEB_025_UNUSED 

SPARE: HSP Only
